Wulingyuan.title: Wulingyuan
Wulingyuan.byline: Wulingyuan (武陵源) is a UNESCO World Heritage Site near the city of Zhangjiajie in Hunan, China.

Wuling Farm.title: Wuling Farm
Wuling Farm.byline: Wuling Recreation Area (Wuling Farm) one of the four recreation areas within Shei-pa National Park, the fifth national park of Taiwan.
